cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on robotic manipulation tasks and training end-to-end visuomotor policies for robots. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a model-free deep reinforcement learning method that leverages demonstration data to assist a reinforcement learning agent. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is another likely category as the policies are trained directly from RGB camera inputs to joint velocities. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a method that combines reinforcement and imitation learning to achieve diverse visuomotor skills. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also a possible category as the paper deals with controlling robotic systems through visuomotor policies.
